node.text:
A collection of moments captured last winter during my time on assignment in Western Greenland, a place so profoundly beautiful but yet alarmingly fragile. 
Location: Greenland - Uummannaq, Saattut, Illussiat.

Music: Icarus by Dexter Britain.

Shot on @sonyalpha.anz A7riii @djiglobal Mavic 2 Pro 
@visitgreenland

node.text:
Flying over the sprawling textures of the Norman River & seasonal flood plains of the Gulf of Carpentaria. It was a true feast for the eyes attempting to capture & untangle the labyrinth of intricate patterns that laid out as we hurled through the air high above. A scene forever etched in my memory..

@queensland #thisisqueensland
